result.name: Farm House Restaurant

reviews.text: Just like the food you eat at home, yummy! Service is excellent.
Excellent, heartier and heavier take on dim sum and seafood.  Their crab roe dumplings 蟹粉小籠包 are a highlight of the dim sum slate.  Very popular relative to its size so book ahead.

A good Chinese restaurant in Causeway Bay, delicious food and good services.  Their 糯米釀雞翼 (fried chicken wing stuffed with sticky rice) is a must try, crispy fried skin with tasty sticky rice inside.  Other dishes and soup are good as well.  Prices are a little bit high but acceptable.
Great food, big plates. We booked for a birthday and were not disappointed. The price is good for the amount and the quality of food. Can totally recommend for an more or less upscale evening.
Good services & delicious food. I think they did not put any MSG on the food.
